---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Returns & Refunds">
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container" style={{ maxWidth: '800px', margin: '0 auto' }}>
      <div class="ui-section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="ui-eyebrow">Our Promise</span>
          <h2>Returns & Refunds</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>We take pride in the quality of our cold-pressed soaps. Because every bar is cured for four weeks and hand-cut, slight variations in color and size are a natural part of the craft.</p>

        <h3>Our Returns Policy</h3>
        <p>Due to the nature of our products and hygiene regulations, we can only accept returns of unused, unopened items in their original packaging within <strong>14 days of delivery</strong>.</p>
        
        <h3>Damaged or Incorrect Orders</h3>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or if you receive the wrong item, please contact us immediately. We will arrange a replacement or full refund right away.</p>

        <h3>How to Return an Item</h3>
        <p>To initiate a return, please visit our <a href="/contact" style={{ color: 'var(--clr-primary)', textDecoration: 'underline' }}>Contact page</a> with your order number. Once authorized, we will provide you with the return address to our Edinburgh studio. Please note that return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the item was faulty.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose { color: var(--clr-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: 1.7; }
  .prose h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--clr-text); margin-top: var(--sp-8); margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); font-weight: 400; }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); }
  .prose strong { color: var(--clr-text); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
